sub_title: Advisor | Business | Communication | Culture | Promotion | Norway | Netherlands
summary: Multilingual (French, English, Dutch and Norwegian) postgraduate in the International Relations. Current position includes handling of Communication, Culture and Business affairs at the Norwegian Embassy in the Hague. Previous experience ranges from organizing Shore Excursions for cruise lines in Norway to Project Management at the European Commission in Brussels, Diplomacy in Morocco and Internet Marketing in the Netherlands. Specialized in International Communication, Online Marketing and International Budget and Grant Management. Solid understanding of cultural diversity and diplomacy.
